### Get all students with default pagination
GET http://localhost:5001/students

### Get students with custom pagination
GET http://localhost:5001/students?page=1&limit=2

### Get specific student
GET http://localhost:5001/students/1

### Get non-existent student
GET http://localhost:5001/students/999

### Create new student
POST http://localhost:5001/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Alice Smith",
    "email": "alice.smith@example.com",
    "age": 24,
    "gender": "female"
}

### Create student with invalid data
POST http://localhost:5001/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "",
    "email": "invalid-email",
    "age": -5,
    "gender": ""
}

### Update student
PUT http://localhost:5001/students/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Updated",
    "age": 25
}

### Update non-existent student
PUT http://localhost:5001/students/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Non Existent"
}

### Delete student
DELETE http://localhost:5001/students/3

### Delete non-existent student
DELETE http://localhost:5001/students/999

